Just ran into this as well. Not sure if it helps, but I put together a small example based on @adambkaplan's repo. For what it's worth not all ignore functionality is broken, but only the "ignore all but X" cases. The example: https://github.com/brancz/dockerignore

```
$ buildah --version
buildah version 1.20.0 (image-spec 1.0.1-dev, runtime-spec 1.0.2-dev)
$ buildah info
{
    "host": {
        "CgroupVersion": "v2",
        "Distribution": {
