```

I may be totally misunderstanding, but it appears to me that the implementation currently can only work with exclusions: https://github.com/containers/buildah/blob/c891ebe41e8e33732c4bb8ca23004e7b4f857cc8/cmd/buildah/addcopy.go#L228-L238
